				<wikidot:authorName>Zyn</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1404533</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <blockquote> <p>'count' applies to discrete items.</p> </blockquote> <p>(chlorophyll a, chlorophyll b, carotenoids? There's over 600 types of carotenoids. Only a handful of kinds of chlorophyll)</p> <p>That said, &quot;concentration&quot; does work better in context, so I'll swap the word in. Thanks!</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
